1
00:00:51,679 --> 00:00:52,480
Grandmother.

2
00:00:52,480 --> 00:00:53,599
Venus

3
00:00:58,039 --> 00:00:58,840
Venus

4
00:01:00,039 --> 00:01:01,480
How are you, my child?

5
00:01:02,719 --> 00:01:05,280
Our nightmare is finally over.

6
00:01:06,960 --> 00:01:07,760
Yes, Grandmother.

7
00:01:08,159 --> 00:01:09,199
Do you know, Venus

8
00:01:10,320 --> 00:01:11,760
I almost didn't get the chance

9
00:01:11,760 --> 00:01:13,119
to see your face again.

10
00:01:14,360 --> 00:01:16,079
If it wasn't for someone

11
00:01:16,079 --> 00:01:17,800
who saved my life.

12
00:01:19,880 --> 00:01:21,280
Who is it, Grandmother?

13
00:01:21,280 --> 00:01:22,000
Venus

14
00:01:24,760 --> 00:01:25,280
Pakin.

15
00:01:37,199 --> 00:01:38,000
Venus

16
00:01:40,679 --> 00:01:41,480
I'm sorry.

17
00:01:44,400 --> 00:01:45,679
For misunderstanding you all this time.

18
00:01:48,360 --> 00:01:49,199
In the past

19
00:01:50,840 --> 00:01:52,400
I've hurt you so much.

20
00:01:53,480 --> 00:01:54,119
If you're angry with me

21
00:01:54,760 --> 00:01:55,719
or if you hate me,

22
00:01:57,679 --> 00:01:58,480
I completely understand.

23
00:02:01,000 --> 00:02:01,800
But at the very leas

24
00:02:03,800 --> 00:02:04,880
please let me say this.

25
00:02:09,840 --> 00:02:10,639
I'm sorry.

26
00:02:13,400 --> 00:02:14,199
I am so sorry.

27
00:02:15,079 --> 00:02:15,840
Venus

28
00:02:26,239 --> 00:02:27,079
And there is one more thing

29
00:02:28,280 --> 00:02:29,119
that I want to tell you.

30
00:02:37,119 --> 00:02:37,920
Venus

31
00:02:40,079 --> 00:02:40,880
I love you.

32
00:04:26,320 --> 00:04:27,119
Lookkai.

33
00:04:28,519 --> 00:04:29,400
Please wake up soon.

34
00:04:33,000 --> 00:04:33,800
I'm waiting for you.

35
00:04:41,360 --> 00:04:42,159
Has he not woken up yet?

36
00:04:45,159 --> 00:04:45,960
Not yet

37
00:04:47,400 --> 00:04:48,199
He still hasn't regained consciousness.

38
00:04:51,199 --> 00:04:53,199
Don't worry, Khun Mavin.

39
00:04:53,840 --> 00:04:54,719
With the power of love

40
00:04:54,719 --> 00:04:56,199
that you have for Lookkai

41
00:04:56,679 --> 00:04:57,480
it will definitely

42
00:04:57,480 --> 00:04:58,360
bring him back to us.

43
00:05:02,960 --> 00:05:03,159
Yes.

44
00:05:04,599 --> 00:05:05,320
Thank you very much.

45
00:05:05,920 --> 00:05:06,760
Khun Venus.

46
00:05:08,199 --> 00:05:09,039
Khun Pakin.

47
00:05:31,639 --> 00:05:32,440
Lookkai! / P'Mavin!

48
00:05:34,000 --> 00:05:34,800
Lookkai!

49
00:05:35,199 --> 00:05:36,199
Lookkai, you're awake!

50
00:05:36,480 --> 00:05:37,199
Lookkai, you're awake!

51
00:05:37,880 --> 00:05:38,760
Lookkai is awake!

52
00:05:39,039 --> 00:05:40,039
He's awake!

53
00:05:46,000 --> 00:05:46,760
Lookkai

54
00:05:50,719 --> 00:05:51,880
Khun Pakin

55
00:05:53,039 --> 00:05:53,760
I know

56
00:05:54,039 --> 00:05:55,079
that you must be angry.

57
00:05:55,519 --> 00:05:56,840
And you must hate me so much

58
00:05:57,800 --> 00:05:59,519
for what I did to Phakinai.

59
00:06:01,639 --> 00:06:03,199
But I want to tell you sincerely

60
00:06:03,960 --> 00:06:05,079
that I never thought

61
00:06:05,679 --> 00:06:06,920
my stupid words

62
00:06:07,800 --> 00:06:09,559
could hurt Pakinai this much.

63
00:06:10,800 --> 00:06:12,159
To the point that he had to
commit suicide.

64
00:06:14,360 --> 00:06:15,519
I was just a fool.

65
00:06:16,719 --> 00:06:17,800
A narcissist.

66
00:06:18,519 --> 00:06:19,320
A selfish person.

67
00:06:20,519 --> 00:06:21,880
I never gave a damn
about anyone else's feelings.

68
00:06:23,599 --> 00:06:24,719
Until the day

69
00:06:25,239 --> 00:06:27,079
I ended up in such a terrible place.

70
00:06:28,079 --> 00:06:29,480
I had to live such a difficult life.

71
00:06:30,480 --> 00:06:31,559
I was looked down upon

72
00:06:32,280 --> 00:06:33,039
scolded

73
00:06:33,760 --> 00:06:34,519
and physically abused.

74
00:06:36,039 --> 00:06:37,280
That's when I finally realized

75
00:06:38,159 --> 00:06:39,280
that what I did to others

76
00:06:39,800 --> 00:06:40,599
was wicked.

77
00:06:40,960 --> 00:06:41,920
How truly evil it was.

78
00:06:47,280 --> 00:06:48,079
Khun Pakin.

79
00:06:48,840 --> 00:06:49,639
I'm sorry.

80
00:06:50,760 --> 00:06:51,639
Please forgive me.

81
00:06:59,239 --> 00:07:00,880
I accept your apology.

82
00:07:05,599 --> 00:07:06,679
But this isn't enough.

83
00:07:10,400 --> 00:07:11,559
What is the meaning of this,
Khun Pakin?

84
00:07:12,320 --> 00:07:13,440
What more do you want?

85
00:07:13,719 --> 00:07:14,239
Do you want to torture

86
00:07:14,239 --> 00:07:15,039
Saturn

87
00:07:15,039 --> 00:07:16,079
just like you tortured me?

88
00:07:16,679 --> 00:07:17,199
No.

89
00:07:19,239 --> 00:07:20,880
Everything that happened to you

90
00:07:21,320 --> 00:07:23,199
was a terrible mistake

91
00:07:24,239 --> 00:07:24,639
Fire

92
00:07:25,199 --> 00:07:26,440
should not be fought with fire.

93
00:07:27,599 --> 00:07:28,599
Vengeance

94
00:07:28,960 --> 00:07:30,519
should only be extinguished
with forgiveness.

95
00:07:31,599 --> 00:07:32,920
Khun Pakin.

96
00:07:33,400 --> 00:07:34,800
Then just tell me.

97
00:07:35,880 --> 00:07:36,920
What do you want me to do?

98
00:07:37,400 --> 00:07:38,519
I am ready to do anything.

99
00:07:39,559 --> 00:07:40,760
If it's enough to pay for the sins

100
00:07:40,760 --> 00:07:42,000
I committed against Pakinai.

101
00:07:42,559 --> 00:07:43,679
I am willing to do it all.

102
00:07:46,239 --> 00:07:47,199
I want you to go meet him.

103
00:07:48,960 --> 00:07:49,639
And tell him

104
00:07:50,119 --> 00:07:50,920
in person.

105
00:07:52,760 --> 00:07:53,920
What do you mean?

106
00:07:57,400 --> 00:07:57,679
Yes.

107
00:07:58,800 --> 00:07:59,760
Pakinai is not dead.

108
00:08:02,000 --> 00:08:02,679
What?!

109
00:08:18,279 --> 00:08:19,079
Nai.

110
00:08:19,920 --> 00:08:20,840
Someone is here to apologize to you.

111
00:08:51,319 --> 00:08:52,439
So this is the reason

112
00:08:52,439 --> 00:08:53,640
you were in such a hurry to see him

113
00:08:53,640 --> 00:08:55,000
which gave you the chance
to save my grandmother's life.

114
00:09:03,560 --> 00:09:04,359
Pakinai.

115
00:09:06,119 --> 00:09:06,920
I am so sorry.

116
00:09:10,760 --> 00:09:11,880
Just as I promised

117
00:09:13,520 --> 00:09:14,880
I will take care of you myself.

118
00:09:17,920 --> 00:09:19,199
And you will recover.

119
00:09:20,920 --> 00:09:22,720
You'll go back to being
the same old Pakinai.

120
00:09:26,720 --> 00:09:29,319
Because how could a Saturn like me

121
00:09:30,359 --> 00:09:32,199
ever exist without its rings like you?

122
00:09:59,520 --> 00:10:00,880
Even though Pakinai hasn't woken up

123
00:10:02,359 --> 00:10:03,159
I am confident

124
00:10:04,600 --> 00:10:06,039
that my brother has forgiven Saturn

125
00:10:07,039 --> 00:10:07,840
with all his heart.

126
00:10:09,239 --> 00:10:10,039
Yes.

127
00:10:10,680 --> 00:10:11,960
Because true love is forgiveness.

128
00:10:16,520 --> 00:10:17,399
And what about you?

129
00:10:18,640 --> 00:10:19,399
Have you forgiven me yet?

130
00:10:28,359 --> 00:10:29,159
Right.

131
00:10:30,399 --> 00:10:31,800
You probably see me as
no different from a beast.

132
00:10:32,880 --> 00:10:33,680
Capable only of violence.

133
00:10:35,960 --> 00:10:36,800
Never knowing what love is.

134
00:10:40,039 --> 00:10:41,000
That's not true at all.

135
00:10:42,680 --> 00:10:43,640
I've never seen you that way.

136
00:10:45,680 --> 00:10:46,439
When I said

137
00:10:46,720 --> 00:10:48,039
that I never forgave you

138
00:10:48,800 --> 00:10:49,800
it wasn't because I didn't love you.

139
00:10:51,000 --> 00:10:51,880
But it's because

140
00:10:51,880 --> 00:10:53,239
I have always understood you.

141
00:10:54,279 --> 00:10:55,760
And I've never been angry at you

142
00:10:56,760 --> 00:10:57,560
held any grudges

143
00:10:58,079 --> 00:10:59,159
or had anything unresolved

144
00:10:59,159 --> 00:11:00,640
that required my forgiveness
in the first place.

145
00:11:15,000 --> 00:11:15,800
Will you marry me?

146
00:11:18,800 --> 00:11:19,840
Yes.

147
00:11:39,800 --> 00:11:41,560
From now on, may both of
my grandchildren

148
00:11:41,560 --> 00:11:43,520
encounter only good things.

149
00:11:44,199 --> 00:11:46,359
May your married life

150
00:11:46,359 --> 00:11:48,319
be like the stars accompanying the sky

151
00:11:48,319 --> 00:11:49,640
for all eternity, my children.

152
00:11:52,279 --> 00:11:54,119
Thank you, Grandmother.

153
00:11:59,640 --> 00:12:00,279
Alright, everyone.

154
00:12:00,920 --> 00:12:02,600
We have now reached the most important moment.

155
00:12:02,880 --> 00:12:03,920
The rings of love

156
00:12:04,199 --> 00:12:05,439
that they are giving to each other

157
00:12:06,199 --> 00:12:07,439
are like a promise.

158
00:12:30,880 --> 00:12:32,960
Come on, everyone, look this way!

159
00:12:37,680 --> 00:12:40,319
1 2 3

160
00:12:56,399 --> 00:12:58,039
They look so lovely, Grandmother.

161
00:13:00,600 --> 00:13:03,159
Ready? 1... 2...

162
00:13:08,560 --> 00:13:11,239
Next couple!

163
00:13:52,159 --> 00:13:52,760
Pakin.

164
00:13:52,760 --> 00:13:53,720
Are you tired today?

165
00:13:54,720 --> 00:13:55,239
Not at all.

166
00:13:55,880 --> 00:13:56,960
I'm so happy today.

167
00:13:56,960 --> 00:13:58,000
And I had the absolute best time.

168
00:13:58,920 --> 00:14:00,000
My only regret is

169
00:14:01,039 --> 00:14:02,800
that Pakinai couldn't be
here for our big day.

170
00:14:05,720 --> 00:14:06,920
But at least

171
00:14:07,560 --> 00:14:09,560
Pakinai got to go back home.

172
00:14:09,560 --> 00:14:11,399
And he has Saturn taking care of him.

173
00:14:11,920 --> 00:14:13,159
And I believe

174
00:14:13,159 --> 00:14:14,079
that one day

175
00:14:14,279 --> 00:14:15,199
he will wake up and become

176
00:14:15,199 --> 00:14:16,640
Saturn's groom for sure.

177
00:14:20,079 --> 00:14:21,319
Just like

178
00:14:22,039 --> 00:14:24,000
how I became Venus's groom.

179
00:14:25,720 --> 00:14:27,359
Now that you're Venus's groom

180
00:14:27,359 --> 00:14:29,039
don't you dare go sneaking
around with anyone else.

181
00:14:31,039 --> 00:14:33,560
There's no one hotter than you anyway.

182
00:14:34,800 --> 00:14:36,000
You better mean it.

183
00:14:37,319 --> 00:14:38,119
I mean it.

184
00:14:49,800 --> 00:14:50,319
What?

185
00:14:50,600 --> 00:14:51,039
Let's go.

186
00:14:51,319 --> 00:14:51,960
Go where?

187
00:14:52,159 --> 00:14:52,760
Come on.

188
00:14:53,520 --> 00:14:54,920
It's still broad daylight!

189
00:14:54,920 --> 00:14:55,680
Get in here.
